# Email Configuration for Firebase Cloud Functions
# This file shows what environment variables you need to set

# Gmail Configuration
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Gmail account
# 2. Create an App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Set these variables:

EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-specific-password

# To set these in Firebase:
# Run: firebase functions:config:set gmail.user="your-email@gmail.com" gmail.password="your-app-password"
# Then deploy: firebase deploy --only functions
